(sorry, no idea, but couldn't resist....)

Options:

Revert to a previous save (If you're using the SAVE mod you'll have one from 30 minutes ago or less by default).

Manually edit your persistent.sfs to fix whatever value got set to 0 and used as the denominator in a calculation for the value that's now NaN.
